notes: URLs point to specific product pages (BU / random-year SKUs). fbp_url: FindBullionPrices comparison page used as fallback when primary scrapes fail. Goldback slugs use format goldback-{state}-g{denom} (STAK-335). Legacy goldback-g{N} slugs retained for frontend backward compat — marked deprecated. Enable vendors one at a time as product URLs are verified.
